Definition: the condition of being unable to perform as a consequence of physical or mental unfitness
Example: reading disability; hearing impairment
Synonyms: adj, all, unfit, disabled, disablement, verb, change, disable, body, handicap, impairment, unfitness, the, condition, of, being, unable, to, perform, as, a, consequence, physical, or, mental, reading, hearing
Category: noun.state
